hopobject.body: The National Gallery slimvia de slabit forum In a sense the pursuit of Fabregas was one which demonstrated how steep is the pair’s learning curve. Those with more experience would have realised before they began it was a non-starter. Sure, on paper, the former Arsenal captain looked an ideal piece of recruitment, providing precisely the kind of drive and purpose from the centre of midfield the current United squad lacks.
